#about
  #whoarewe
    h3
      | Who are we?
    br
  #about-cards
    
    #progressive.demo-card-square.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp
      .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
        h2.mdl-card__title-text Progressive
      .mdl-card__supporting-text
        | Elite Global Language Learning Center was established in 2009 as a premier 
        | language instruction center for children aged 6 and above. We focus on building
        | strong foundational writing, speaking and grammar skills that will
        | prepare our students for life-long independent learning.
    
    #fun.demo-card-square.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp
      .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
        h2.mdl-card__title-text Fun
      .mdl-card__supporting-text
        | Elite encourages a positive and creative dynamic between students while providing a supportive environment for teachers and a conducive
        | study environment for students. Students eagerly look forward to attending
        | their classes and make new friends in the process. 
        
    
      
    #map.demo-card-square.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp
      .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
        h2.mdl-card__title-text Centrally located
      .mdl-card__supporting-text
        | Located in the heart of the Hartamas/Mont Kiara area,
        | we are easily accessible from downtown via Jalan Kuching
        | as well as from PJ via Sprint Highway. 
      .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
        a(href='https://www.google.com.my/maps/place/Elite+Global+Language+Learning+Centre/@3.1603074,101.648098,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x31cc48f01d782037:0xc2c66c4e5cadb604!8m2!3d3.160302!4d101.650292?hl=en', target='_blank').mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect
          | View Map
