#apply
  #interested
    h3 Yes, I'm interested!
    p#blurb
      | Your responsibilities will include general administrative tasks
      | including coordinating pick-up and drop service and fielding calls
      | from parents. Don't worry, we'll always be on hand for you to ask questions 
      | and to provide you with the necessary guidance. There won't a dull moment at Elite
      | and we guarantee you'll learn a wealth of transferrable skills!
      | The duration of employment in the first instance will be for the holiday programme
      | for the months of July and August. Thereafter, there is a possibility for staying on 
      | as a part-time or even a full-time staff.
      | Simply fill out the 3-page form below and we'll get back to you ASAP!
    #scroll
     form#myform(method='post', enctype='multipart/form-data', action='')
      #container
        #contact.appcards.demo-card-square.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp
          .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
            h2.mdl-card__title-text Contact details
          .mdl-card__supporting-text
            .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield
              input#firstName.mdl-textfield__input(type='text', required='', name='firstName')
              label.mdl-textfield__label(for='firstName') First Name
            .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield
              input#lastName.mdl-textfield__input(type='text', required='', name = 'lastName')
              label.mdl-textfield__label(for='lastName') Last Name
            .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield
              input#email.mdl-textfield__input(type='text', required='', name = 'email')
              label.mdl-textfield__label(for='email') E-mail
            .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield
              input#phone.mdl-textfield__input(type='text', required='', name = 'phone')
              label.mdl-textfield__label(for='phone') Phone #
          .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
            a.next.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect
              | Next
        #essay.appcards.demo-card-square.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.none
          .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
            h2.mdl-card__title-text Essay
          .mdl-card__supporting-text
            | Tell us something about yourself, e.g. your hobbies, or why you're applying to this job. Writing in Korean is not necessary, but we're sure you'd like to show off your skills!
            .mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield
              textarea#essaytext.mdl-textfield__input(type='text', rows='8', name = 'essaytext')
              label.mdl-textfield__label(for='essaytext') Start here!
            //
              <div class="mdl-textfield mdl-js-textfield" id="essaytext-expanded">
              <textarea class="mdl-textfield__input" type="text" rows= "3"  ></textarea>
              <label class="mdl-textfield__label" for="essaytext">Start here!</label>
              </div>
          .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
            a.next.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect
              | Next
        #resume.appcards.demo-card-square.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.none
          .mdl-card__title.mdl-card--expand
            h2.mdl-card__title-text Resume (optional)
          .mdl-card__supporting-text
            | Please upload your resume, if you have one handy, otherwise don't sweat it. You can bring it along at the interview.
            #uploadelements
              #resume_upload_button
                label.mdl-button.mdl-js-button.mdl-button--fab.mdl-js-ripple-effect.mdl-button--colored
                  i.material-icons file_upload
                  input#resumeupload.none(type='file', name='resume')
                  // .none = display: none
              #file-input-text-div.mdl-textfield.mdl-js-textfield
                input#file_input_text.file_input_text.mdl-textfield__input(type='text', disabled='', readonly='')
                label.mdl-textfield__label(for='file_input_text')
          .mdl-card__actions.mdl-card--border
            a.next.submit.mdl-button.mdl-button--colored.mdl-js-button.mdl-js-ripple-effect
              | submit
        #success.appcards.demo-card-square.mdl-card.mdl-shadow--2dp.none
          h2 Thanks for your application.
          h3 We'll be in touch ASAP!
